<para id="fs-id1423125">Rikki earned <m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>$87</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math> commission when she sold a <m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>$1,450</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math> stove. What rate of commission did she get?</para>
